data.description: Investor special! A little TLC goes a long way! Priced to sell and located in the cute little town of Flushing, this two bedroom one bathroom ranch has so much potential. Some features include: a fireplace located in the living room, double lot with a fenced in spacious backyard and storage shed in the carport, an additional shed in the backyard, and house located on a dead end street close to downtown.  New roof (2020) Bathroom vanity and flooring (2023) Paint 3rd bedroom (2024) Mechanical updates include:  Furnace and AC condenser (2022). Water heater (2014). Main bedroom has potential walk in closet.  Turn this into a high end rental or renovate and move in! Call for your showing today!
